headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Eaton (ETN) After 123% Three Year Share Price Surge?
summary: If you are wondering whether Eaton's current share price gives you good value or is asking too much, this article will walk through what the numbers are really saying about the stock. Eaton recently closed at US$374.56, with returns of 13.1% over the last 30 days, 14.4% year to date, 31.9% over 1 year and 123.5% over 3 years, which naturally raises questions about how much future upside or risk is already reflected in the price. These moves have kept Eaton on many investors' watchlists,...

headline: How The Eaton (ETN) Narrative Is Shifting As Analysts Rework Growth And Valuation Assumptions
summary: Eaton’s updated fair value estimate has shifted from US$403.80 to US$407.53, a move of about US$3.73 per share that reflects refreshed modeling rather than a wholesale change in story. This adjustment lines up with a mixed set of analyst reactions, where some firms are lifting targets and ratings while others are trimming expectations around the edges as they refine their earnings and valuation work. As you read on, you will see how these moving targets shape the narrative you are watching...

headline: The Stock That Didn’t Get Crushed by the AI Doomsday Essay
summary: Monday was a tough day for the stock market.  One factor hitting the stocks on Monday was an essay from Citrini Research, published on Sunday, that imagines a future in which AI devastates the economy.

headline: Meta strikes AI chip deal with AMD days after committing to deploy millions of Nvidia GPUs
summary: AMD has secured Meta as a customer for its Helios rack-scale system, as Nvidia's Blackwell faces heightened competition.
